OL,3,CJuror denies misconduct charge after
OL,4,Cschool stabbing trial collapsed
OL,6,FA jury member has denied a charge
OL,7,Frelating to the collapse of a school
OL,8,Fstabbing trial.
OL,10,FChristopher Elias, 45, appeared before
OL,11,FCardiff Crown Court accused of
OL,12,Fprohibited conduct by a juror on a
OL,13,Fdate between 29 September and 10
OL,14,FOctober last year.
OL,16,FThe charge relates to the collapse of
OL,17,Fthe first Ammanford school stabbing
OL,18,Ftrial, after a young girl attempted to
OL,19,Fmurder two teachers and a fellow pupil
OL,20,Fat Ysgol Dyffryn Aman in April 2024.
