OL,3,CJuror denies misconduct charge after
OL,4,Cschool stabbing trial collapsed
OL,6,FA teenage girl, who cannot be named
OL,7,Ffor legal reasons, was sentenced to 15
OL,8,Fyears' detention earlier this year for
OL,9,Fthe attempted murder of Fiona Elias,
OL,10,FLiz Hopkin and the pupil at the school
OL,11,Ffollowing a retrial.
OL,13,FThe first trial collapsed in October
OL,14,Flast year, with the judge saying there
OL,15,Fhad been a "great irregularity in the
OL,16,Fjury".
OL,18,FElias, of Millbank, Waunceirch, Neath
OL,19,FPort Talbot, spoke only to confirm his
OL,20,Fdate of birth, address and enter his
OL,21,Fnot guilty plea.
